April 18, 2008Qingdao (People.com), April 18th (Song Xuechun Li Peiqiang) - Pingdu City, Shandong Province integrated the issuance and implementation of standards from the Ministry of Finance. Since last year, the city's teaching center's teacher resource training base and Pingdu City's finance department jointly held the continuing education training class for accountants.The training content is "business accounting standards" and "internal accounting control systems."Three days in one period, so far there have been a total of 14 periods - more than 7000 working accountants are trained.Through the training and exam, accountants improve their professional skills and theoretical knowledge, allowing working accountants to quickly become familiar with and get a grasp of the relevant rules of new business accounting standards.